text: Cajsa Stina (CajsaStina) Åkerström, born 16 August 1967 in Stockholm, Sweden, is a Swedish singer, songwriter and author. She is the daughter of singer Fred Åkerström. She participated at Melodifestivalen 2014 in the third semifinal. Her song was called "En enkel sång". == References == ==Other websites== *Official website Category:1967 births Category:Swedish singers Category:Swedish writers Category:Living people
